## Overview
Add provenance metadata to the SearchHit struct so search results carry
source information for display and further processing.

## Implementation Details

### SearchHit Extension
In `src/lib.rs`, extend the SearchHit struct:
```rust
#[derive(Debug, Clone, Serialize, Deserialize)]
pub struct SearchHit {
    // ... existing fields
    pub conversation_id: String,
    pub agent: String,
    pub workspace: String,
    pub snippet: String,
    pub score: f32,
    pub timestamp: DateTime<Utc>,

    // New provenance fields
    pub source_hostname: Option<String>,
    pub source_type: SourceType,
    pub sync_timestamp: Option<DateTime<Utc>>,
}

#[derive(Debug, Clone, Serialize, Deserialize, Default)]
pub enum SourceType {
    #[default]
    Local,
    Remote,
}
